summary: I just got accused by someone of not liking Jon/Dany because of the incest and trust me, that honestly has nothing to do with...
body: I just got accused by someone of not liking Jon/Dany because of the incest and trust me, that honestly has nothing to do with it. It’s not even about the characters, really, I just really don’t feel the chemistry between Kit and Emilia. To me they’re the two most boring people on the show and putting them together is a snooze. And I understand that they have limited time but the whole thing felt so rushed to me. Idk, I feel like they could have done more but they made everything between them so serious and boring. I honestly feel like Yara and Dany had more chemistry in 3 minutes than Jon and Dany had in an entire season. That’s just my opinion though, I know other people feel differently about Jon/Dany which is fine, whatever works for them. It just doesn’t really appeal to me personally.

summary: Since I shared the effects guy saying he’d be working on GoT until May the other day, I thought I should also share the follow...
body:
Since I shared the effects guy saying he’d be working on GoT until May the other day, I thought I should also share the follow up (linked below). James Hibberd at EW is known as D&Ds mouthpiece, and he was quick to state that they are still aiming for Emmys submission in 2019 in the season 8 footage article:

https://ew.com/tv/2018/08/26/game-of-thrones-season-8-footage/

Seems this was put out in response to the first claim, so fingers crossed it’s coming in Spring and we can all be released from this terrible limbo.

summary: I don’t understand why everyone seems to hate Sansa Stark because even though she was childish at first all she’s done since,...
body: I don’t understand why everyone seems to hate Sansa Stark because even though she was childish at first all she’s done since, like, season two is adapt and try to survive after being a prisoner, then a fugitive, then a prisoner again. Since getting back to winterfell she’s done nothing but make sure her people are safe and I don’t see why people say she’s trying to steal Jon’s throne she just wants to survive the winter and the war. She has suffered to get where she is now and she better not die in season eight
